## JWT (hammer-userмЩА лПЩмЭЉнХімХЉ нХ®)
Jwt__Issuer=hammer-user
Jwt__Audience=hammer
Jwt__SecretKey=your-secret-key-must-be-at-least-32-bytes-long!!

## Redis
Redis__ConnectionString=localhost:6379,abortConnect=false

## Kafka
Kafka__BootstrapServers=localhost:9092

## Rate Limiting
RateLimiting__PermitLimit=100
RateLimiting__WindowSeconds=60

## CORS
Cors__AllowedOrigins__0=http://localhost:3000
